24:44.276 --> 24:46.653
LAKE: Okay...
[sparking]

24:46.653 --> 24:48.864
Ready to blow the roof off this place?

24:48.864 --> 24:51.116
‐ Sure.
[all chattering]

24:53.368 --> 24:59.291
‐ ♪ They were here first ♪

24:59.291 --> 25:00.751
[fireworks whistling]

25:00.751 --> 25:03.253
