♪ Oily marks ♪

25:27.694 --> 25:31.490
♪ Appear on walls ♪

25:31.490 --> 25:35.994
♪ Where pleasure moments ♪

25:35.994 --> 25:39.331
♪ Hung before ♪

25:39.331 --> 25:43.126
♪ The takeover ♪

25:43.126 --> 25:48.006
♪ The sweeping insensitivity ♪

25:48.006 --> 25:50.133
‐ So, are you excited for your last day
at Brasstown tomorrow?

25:50.133 --> 25:51.552
‐ Yeah. Yeah, uh, hey,

25:51.552 --> 25:53.512
I, I know the summer rush will be over,

25:53.512 --> 25:55.848
but is there any chance I can,
I don't know, keep working there?

25:55.848 --> 25:57.474
I mean, pick up a few extra shifts.

25:57.474 --> 25:59.726
I need the extra cash.
Dating Lake is not cheap.

25:59.726 --> 26:02.855
‐ [laughs] I don't know if they have
any openings, but I'll ask.

26:02.855 --> 26:04.022
‐ Thanks.

26:09.444 --> 26:12.197
‐ Hey, Mom. How you feeling?

26:12.197 --> 26:15.325
‐ ♪ Spin me 'round again ♪

26:15.325 --> 26:16.660
FELIX: Did you eat?

26:17.619 --> 26:19.621
‐ No. I'm not hungry.

26:20.289 --> 26:21.957
‐ You gotta eat, Mom.

26:23.125 --> 26:24.585
I'll heat you up some soup.

26:25.544 --> 26:29.756
‐ ♪ When busy streets ♪

26:29.756 --> 26:32.968
♪ Amass with people ♪

26:32.968 --> 26:35.846
♪ Would stop to hold ♪

26:35.846 --> 26:39.933
♪ Their heads heavy ♪

26:42.102 --> 26:43.937
♪ What'd you say? ♪

26:44.730 --> 26:47.900
♪ That you only meant well ♪
VICTOR: Hi.

26:47.900 --> 26:51.778
‐ Hi, mijo. Did you have fun
with your friends?

26:51.778 --> 26:54.323
‐ Yeah. Yeah, we had a good time.

26:54.323 --> 26:56.366
Mom?
‐ Yeah?

26:57.492 --> 26:59.453
‐ Benji is my boyfriend,

26:59.453 --> 27:01.079
and I'd like you to call him that.

27:04.958 --> 27:06.335
You have a good night.

27:07.878 --> 27:11.965
‐ ♪ Mmm, what did you say? ♪

27:11.965 --> 27:13.050
[exhales]

27:17.554 --> 27:20.682
♪ What what what did you say? ♪

